expression.expression:
CASE
        WHEN LOWER(TRIM(pdopdj)) IS NULL OR TRIM(pddrqj) = '' OR TRIM(pddrqj) = '0' THEN NULL 
        ELSE to_timestamp(
            CONCAT(
                CAST(SUBSTR(TRIM(pddrqj), 1, 4) AS VARCHAR(4)),
                '-',
                CAST(SUBSTR(TRIM(pddrqj), 5, 2) AS VARCHAR(2)),
                '-',
                CAST(SUBSTR(TRIM(pddrqj), 7, 2) AS VARCHAR(2))
            ),
            'yyyy-MM-dd'
        )
    END

CASE
        WHEN LOWER(TRIM(pdopdj)) IS NULL OR TRIM(pdopdj) = '' OR TRIM(pdopdj) = '0' THEN NULL

            CONCAT(
                CAST(SUBSTR(TRIM(pdopdj), 1, 4) AS VARCHAR(4)),
                '-',
                CAST(SUBSTR(TRIM(pdopdj), 5, 2) AS VARCHAR(2)),
                '-',
                CAST(SUBSTR(TRIM(pdopdj), 7, 2) AS VARCHAR(2))
            ),
            'yyyy-MM-dd'
        )
    END
